Constructors:
- help us create the object from the classes in a more secure and neat way. We can also put any piece of code
that we want to execute when the object of a class is created.
Why we should use Constructors?
1) They help use write more secure classes
2) Cleaner code
3) More control over the values that we can assign to the instance fields.
Syntax:
1)Usually
2) Same name as class name
3) No return type not even void
4) Parameters
5) Body of the constructor.



















